lp. Bonus: It has a bright, invigorating fragrance that’s both woody and citrusy.Advertisement - Continue Reading Below5Kérastase Genesis Strengthening Shampoo for Normal to Oily HairEveryone needs a reliable shampoo in their life. In addition to gently cleansing the scalp and removing buildup, this nourishing gel formula strengthens hair that’s been subjected to heat damage and over-brushing. It also moisturizes and detangles, thanks to edelweiss native cells and ginger root. Consider incorporating it into your routine if you have an oily scalp, damage, or thinning. 6Kérastase Chronologiste Mask for Dull and Brittle HairDryness and damage (think split ends and breakage) are no match for this super-rich and nourishing hair mask. The deeply restorative product is powered by a trio of high-end ingredients: hyaluronic acid to moisturize and hydrate, vitamin E to help protect against external environmental aggressors, and abyssine to enhance volume and bounce. You can use it as a conditioner or a weekly treatment for soft, smooth, shiny hair.",
